    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=RFK24&amp;title=Holdouts\" rel=\"nofollow\">Holdouts</a> can be created with the PrmanHoldoutCreate macro.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"505\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179038/rfkHoldouts.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531539865&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=505&amp;height=400\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179038/rfkHoldouts.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531539865&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"505\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179054\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkHoldouts.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179038\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"f5d5f6c6-fc24-4e7b-9d4c-a3e49615e4c4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179038/rfkHoldouts.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531539865&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=505&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179038/rfkHoldouts.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531539865&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=505&amp;height=400 1x\"></span><p> The PrmanHoldoutCreate macro has several parameters to control the behavior of the render:</p><p><strong>holdoutGeo</strong>: Add all the geometry that you want to act as a holdout here.</p><p><strong>Mode</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Off: Turn off holdout workflow. Ignore this macro.</p></li><li><p>Composite: Composite the holdout image over the background image specified in the imagePlaneSettings.</p></li><li><p>No Composite: Create the holdout image without compositing the background image.</p></li></ul><p><strong>outputAOVs</strong>: Write the shadow and occluded AOVs to the renderLocation. The image names will be holdout_shadowAOV.exr and holdout_occludedAOV.exr.</p><p><strong>renderLocation</strong>: Render directory for the shadow and occluded AOVs. The renderLocation is set to $KATANA_TMPDIR unless otherwise specified. This parameter is available when outputAOVs is checked.</p><p><strong>imagePlaneSettings</strong>: The Filename parameter is where you will specify the background image.  All the settings in this group are the same parameters on the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=RFK24&amp;title=PxrImageDisplayFilter\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrImageDisplayFilter</a>. The macro uses this sample filter to composite the holdout image and shadow AOV over the background image.</p>"
    }
  },
